verses.verse: <S%H1984>Praise<s%> the <S%H3050>Lord!<s%> <S%H1984>Praise,<s%> O <S%H5650>servants<s%> of the <S%H3068>Lord.<s%> <S%H1984>Praise<s%> the <S%H8034>name<s%> of the <S%H3068>Lord.<s%>
<S%H1288>Blessed<s%> be the <S%H8034>name<s%> of the <S%H3068>Lord<s%> From <S%H6258>this<s%> <S%H6258>time<s%> forth and <S%H5704>forever.<s%> <S%H5769><s%>
From the <S%H4217>rising<s%> of the <S%H8121>sun<s%> to its <S%H3996>setting<s%> The <S%H8034>name<s%> of the <S%H3068>Lord<s%> is to be <S%H1984>praised.<s%>
<S%H4310>Who<s%> is like the <S%H3068>Lord<s%> our <S%H430>God,<s%> Who is <S%H3427>enthroned<s%> on <S%H1361>high,<s%>
Who <S%H8213>humbles<s%> Himself to <S%H7200>behold<s%> [The things that are] in <S%H8064>heaven<s%> and in the <S%H776>earth<s%>?
He <S%H6965>raises<s%> the <S%H1800>poor<s%> from the <S%H6083>dust,<s%> And <S%H7311>lifts<s%> the <S%H34>needy<s%> from the <S%H830>ash<s%> <S%H6083>heap,<s%>
To make [them] <S%H3427>sit<s%> with <S%H5081>princes,<s%> With the <S%H5081>princes<s%> of His <S%H5971>people.<s%>

He makes the <S%H6135>barren<s%> <S%H6135>woman<s%> <S%H3427>abide<s%> in the <S%H1004>house<s%> [As] a <S%H8056>joyful<s%> <S%H517>mother<s%> of <S%H1121>children.<s%> <S%H1984>Praise<s%> the <S%H3050>Lord!<s%>
